      "comment": "Keen on FORGING AHEAD (10) over the extra ground. Former Qld galloper who has had two sharp races for the new yard but now gets to a winnable trip. Last time at the mile was runner-up at Doomben. Expecting huge improvement. FRANKFURT (1) was a close-up fourth this trip two back then safely held over 1300m latest. Will appreciate getting back to the mile. COLLISON (7) was in the firing line on the turn and finished second last start over 1300m at this track, beaten a neck. Nicely placed to go one better. FABERGE TZAR (5) was fair last time this trip and can finish closer.",
